data.description: Price Improvement. Priced to Sell. There is room for credits for painting and minor cosmetic repairs. Water heater 5 years old roof 10 years old windows 3 years old.  Charming Ranch- Style home that's the epitome of comfort and style. This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom residence is a true gum offering a blend of classic elegance and modern convenience. Step inside to discover a spacious and inviting formal living room perfect for gathering. The adjacent dining area provides an ideal setting for special meals with loved one. But that's just the beginning! One of the highlights of this home is the delightful screened in porch, where you can enjoy the fresh air and lovely views all year round. Recently installed windows, fresh paint and so much more to offer, this property is a must see. Come to see before its sold. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours.
